SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from :1/MQHI where MQHI_HOFF_CODE = ':2' and MQHI_MQTY_ID = 59 and YEAR(MQHI_DELETED_DATE) = YEAR(':3') and MONTH(MQHI_DELETED_DATE) = MONTH(':3')

select count(*) from :1/CLHS, :1/CLNT where CLNT101_ADMNO = CLHS_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = CLHS_CLNTNO and SUBSTRING(CLHS_DATCHANGED,1,4) = YEAR(':2') and SUBSTRING(CLHS_DATCHANGED,5,2) = MONTH(':2') and CLHS_TYPE = 'F' and CLNT203_OFFICE = ':3'
